l":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/14\/blackseed-cure-except-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":26810,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Healing properties of blackseed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 14, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"This blackseed is healing for all diseases but poison.\u201d She said, \u201cWhat is poison?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cDeath.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5363 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0627\u0626\u0634\u0629 \u0642\u0627\u0644\u062a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5460,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/21\/honey-treatment-upset-stomach\/","url_meta":{"origin":26810,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Honey: The Prophet uses honey to treat upset stomach","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa'id al-Khudri reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \"My brother has diarrhea.\" The Prophet said, \"Give him honey to drink.\" The man gave him honey to drink and he said, \"I gave it to him but his diarrhea only\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41237,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/27\/allah-removes-pain\/","url_meta":{"origin":26810,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ruqyah: Calling upon Allah alone to remove pain","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 27, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abd al-Aziz reported: Thabit and I entered the home of Anas ibn Malik, and Thabit said, \u201cO Abu Hamzah, I am complaining of pain.\u201d Anas said, \u201cShall I not invoke over you with the incantation of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him?\u201d Thabit said, \u201cOf course.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32706,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/all-cures-but-aging\/","url_meta":{"origin":26810,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Allah placed cures for all diseases, except aging","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Sharik reported: A bedouin said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, shall we not seek treatment?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYes, O servants of Allah, seek treatment. Verily, Allah did not place a disease but that he also placed its treatment or cure, except for one ailment.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35724,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/20\/quran-honey\/","url_meta":{"origin":26810,"position":5},"title":"Abdullah on Medicine: Use the Quran and honey for healing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Ahwas reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cYou must make use of two healers: the Quran and honey.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 2345 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bayhaqi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0635\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u0650\u0641\u064e\u0627\u0626\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0622\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26810","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":tru